Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Mix SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, cream cheese, bananas and vanilla in a medium mixing bowl using a hand mixer. Mix until creamy. Place crescent rolls on an ungreased baking sheet. Spread about 1 tablespoon of filling onto each crescent roll and roll into crescent shape. Bake in preheated oven 12 to 15 minutes or until lightly browned.